<title>UK: UK's Hepworth names J.F. Chene as new chief.</title>
<headline>UK's Hepworth names J.F. Chene as new chief.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>British building products company Hepworth Plc named on Wednesday Jean-Francois Chene as chief executive from October 1, 1997.</p>
<p>Chene chairs white goods manufacturer Brandt SA.  </p>
<p>Chene, 43, was previously employed by Hepworth from 1990 to 1996 as managing director of its boiler division, Saunier Duval.</p>
<p>Chene will be based in Hepworth's London head office which has recently relocated from Sheffield.</p>
